text: Lisa Cano Burkhead (born 1970 or 1971) is an American educator and politician. She was the 36th Lieutenant Governor of Nevada from 2021 to 2022. She was nominated by Governor Steve Sisolak to replace Kate Marshall. ==References== Category:1970s births Category:Living people Category:Lieutenant Governors of Nevada Category:Politicians from Las Vegas Category:Educators from Las Vegas Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians
